tweet: b'You can do it afraid! That means that you can feel afraid, but still go ahead and do what you believe God wants you to do. #JoyceQuote'

b'Are you worrying about tomorrow when you should be focusing on today? Trust God to equip you for whatever comes today, tomorrow, and in the future, so that you can receive the fullness of His gifts today. https://t.co/9TS3hS12lu'

b'In 2021, when people called for help, you responded. Whether it was the earthquake in Haiti, wildfires in California, or civil unrest in Israel, you demonstrated the love of Jesus Christ.\n\nRead the stories of people who were helped in a time of need at https://t.co/EGZEsd4TO0 https://t.co/gn2490tGvP'

b'God is bigger than any attack of the enemy, bigger than your worries, your problems and your fears. b'All we really need to be happy is God! #JoyceQuote'

b'Do you have what the enemy is telling you is an impossible situation? I want to remind you today that all things are possible with God. #JoyceQuote'
